title: Country Artist Writes Song Inspired By Bobby + Did Lunchbox Take Tesla To His High School Reunion?

A country artist is including a song on his upcoming album that was inspired by Bobby. Lunchbox recaps his high school reunion and tells us if he drove Brooklyn Decker’s Tesla. Also, Bobby interviews The Bachelorette Hannah B.
